Package org.deri.any23.mime

This package provides support for MIME type data detection.

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
MIMETypeDetector This detector is able to estimate the MIME type of some given raw data.
 

Class Summary
MIMEType A MIME type with an optional q (quality) value.
NaiveMIMETypeDetector Basic implementation of MIMETypeDetector based on file extensions.
TikaMIMETypeDetector Implementation of MIMETypeDetector based on Apache Tika.
